<!-- {"session_id":"8c0d48e5-1d74-4784-9e75-9b413a5983e4","transcript_path":"/Users/yabo/.claude/projects/-Users-yabo-Documents-Code-phone-to-laptop/8c0d48e5-1d74-4784-9e75-9b413a5983e4.jsonl","cwd":"/Users/yabo/Documents/Code/phone-to-laptop","hook_event_name":"PostToolUse","tool_name":"Write","tool_input":{"file_path":"/Users/yabo/Documents/Code/phone-to-laptop/tests/test_auto_detect_limit.md","content":"# Test: Limited Auto-Detect (English/Bulgarian only)\n\n## Test Case 1: English Voice Message\n\n**Arrange:**\n- Set language to \"auto\" in bot settings\n- Prepare English voice message\n\n**Act:**\n- Send English voice message saying \"Hello, this is a test\"\n\n**Assert:**\n- Language detected as \"en\"\n- Text transcribed correctly in English\n- No translation provided (since it's already English)\n\n## Test Case 2: Bulgarian Voice Message\n\n**Arrange:**\n- Set language to \"auto\" in bot settings\n- Prepare Bulgarian voice message\n\n**Act:**\n- Send Bulgarian voice message saying \"Здравей, това е тест\"\n\n**Assert:**\n- Language detected as \"bg\"\n- Text transcribed correctly in Bulgarian\n- English translation provided\n\n## Test Case 3: Other Language (e.g., Spanish)\n\n**Arrange:**\n- Set language to \"auto\" in bot settings\n- Prepare Spanish voice message\n\n**Act:**\n- Send Spanish voice message saying \"Hola, esto es una prueba\"\n\n**Assert:**\n- System detects it's not English or Bulgarian\n- Falls back to English transcription\n- May produce incorrect/garbled transcription (expected behavior)\n- Logs show: \"Detected es, not en/bg. Forcing English transcription.\"\n\n## Implementation Details\n\nThe auto-detect now works as follows:\n1. First attempts auto-detection with Whisper\n2. If detected language is \"en\" or \"bg\", uses that result\n3. If detected language is anything else, re-runs with forced English\n4. This limits auto-detect to only English and Bulgarian languages"},"tool_response":{"type":"create","filePath":"/Users/yabo/Documents/Code/phone-to-laptop/tests/test_auto_detect_limit.md","content":"# Test: Limited Auto-Detect (English/Bulgarian only)\n\n## Test Case 1: English Voice Message\n\n**Arrange:**\n- Set language to \"auto\" in bot settings\n- Prepare English voice message\n\n**Act:**\n- Send English voice message saying \"Hello, this is a test\"\n\n**Assert:**\n- Language detected as \"en\"\n- Text transcribed correctly in English\n- No translation provided (since it's already English)\n\n## Test Case 2: Bulgarian Voice Message\n\n**Arrange:**\n- Set language to \"auto\" in bot settings\n- Prepare Bulgarian voice message\n\n**Act:**\n- Send Bulgarian voice message saying \"Здравей, това е тест\"\n\n**Assert:**\n- Language detected as \"bg\"\n- Text transcribed correctly in Bulgarian\n- English translation provided\n\n## Test Case 3: Other Language (e.g., Spanish)\n\n**Arrange:**\n- Set language to \"auto\" in bot settings\n- Prepare Spanish voice message\n\n**Act:**\n- Send Spanish voice message saying \"Hola, esto es una prueba\"\n\n**Assert:**\n- System detects it's not English or Bulgarian\n- Falls back to English transcription\n- May produce incorrect/garbled transcription (expected behavior)\n- Logs show: \"Detected es, not en/bg. Forcing English transcription.\"\n\n## Implementation Details\n\nThe auto-detect now works as follows:\n1. First attempts auto-detection with Whisper\n2. If detected language is \"en\" or \"bg\", uses that result\n3. If detected language is anything else, re-runs with forced English\n4. This limits auto-detect to only English and Bulgarian languages","structuredPatch":[]}} -->
