## Done! Auto-detect is now limited to English and Bulgarian

When you set the language to "**Auto-detect**":
- **English** voice messages → Transcribed as English
- **Bulgarian** voice messages → Transcribed as Bulgarian with English translation
- **Any other language** → Forced to English transcription (may be inaccurate)

The bot will log when it detects a non-English/Bulgarian language and forces English transcription.

